       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">最近几天，有一部电影在社交网站上很火――</span><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">《湄公河行动》</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="1.4018691588785046" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANcGUVbsElhIp2OGibxBfJIMBI0sGDcmJaXBqzBaaZKMeUP0WVRdMwjibA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="428" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">豆瓣评分8.2，票房一路逆袭，超过了同档期的几部大烂片。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="1.0227272727272727" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANPNybJYLfg9PTRxHgF6wfbZw86XMdriaXXeuelsXIyNdckaib8v5h5YkQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="264" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">哥还没看这部电影，在这里就不作评价。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但电影改编的真实事件――10.5湄公河惨案，却是哥重点想说的。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">时间要回到5年前。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2011年10月5日，两艘中国船舶华平号和玉兴8号，正朝泰国的清盛码头驶去，船上13名船员并不知道，厄运即将来临。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">当天9时左右，两艘船在湄公河遭到了武装快艇的劫持，七八名毒贩登船后，蒙上船员的眼睛，又把上千万的毒品搬上了船。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.5451263537906137" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuAN27R5RfvrL2be5zrFcnlC6DFkmdW5YLjmibDPr1ibdDVvVQ90nAOUf9sw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">几个小时之后，得知船上有大量毒品，泰国军方朝华平号和玉兴8号赶来，他们要击毙“贩毒”的中国船员。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANEXVtV1JckaEHYUzfZyEZhsHNT6DZS1AA8NrFFTwQQrPkAibbq8fuhyA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="484" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">泰国警方进入现场勘查时，发现船上血迹斑斑，布满弹孔。12名中国船员失踪不见，只有一名船员的尸体。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.6321138211382114" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANReQfZEvqicJpibcA5Hx71AQNXpnUADAuoI98ZXuluy8Vh7kkgj4bqicxQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="492" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">第二天，泰国警方向媒体展示了缴获的毒品，称在两艘船上共缴获91.8万颗冰毒，价值两千多万人民币。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">直到案发第三天，中国船员的尸体才被打捞上岸，遗体惨不忍睹。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.6285714285714286" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANkfCbv1H6BWauultHic2Kk87IHibbksiaHMLrHJHtdS1ddwdpSAot2VCug/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="490" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">所有船员双手被反绑，蒙眼、蒙嘴，身上布满枪眼和刀伤。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.7505376344086021" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANOSxuLFF5qWTYWV3tib9hNWYUehicQeKBNtMSN0Q5hicewFOjOnJR9vseA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="465" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">湄公河一名参与尸体打捞工作的船员回忆道：“很多人身上被打了两三枪，几乎每一枪都是致命的，头部、胸部、颈部都有枪眼，如果仅仅是为了杀人夺命，那没必要开这么多枪。”<span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">（《三联生活周刊》）</span></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.6536082474226804" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANxpnjLxicdBRU1XqtibWGHbOP54ox97vXCmHUZsXPSIRRuNL9tiaYQvVzA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="485" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">事实上，船上运载的根本不是毒品，毒品是“糯康集团”用于嫁祸中国船员放上去的。13名船员也没有失踪，而是全部被杀害。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">而“糯康集团”的头领――糯康，就是这次惨案的幕后黑手。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="1.127659574468085" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANnRYUfCCx3R2p77yziaWgWgvJDv4KniaxDWNuE6CYEzOyuUFpmgviaribUw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="282" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">糯康跟这些船员</span><span style="font-size:auto; line-height: 28.8px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">究竟</span><span style="font-size:auto; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">有什么仇，要如此残忍杀害他们？</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">还得从头说起。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">缅甸人糯康年轻时跟随大毒枭坤沙，而坤沙是前蒙泰军总指挥，因制造海洛因而闻名世界。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.8850574712643678" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuAN9XDibibQ7RYesUQfJph9tldH9VgH3sibFlNJqWFROnziaS2ew7w5ccnF7Q/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="348" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1996年，坤沙向缅甸政府军投降，而糯康却选择从事毒品生意，大有成为坤沙继承者的势头。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">糯康珠江将自己的势力范围扩大到湄公河流域，<strong style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他要求所有过往船只都要交税，当地的赌场也要向他交“保护费”。不仅如此，糯康还绑架、贩卖人口，通过贩卖人口每年可赚上千万美元。</strong></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></strong></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="line-height: 28.8px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">可谓是无恶不作。</span></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.67" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANVqVCsyYpt6h7j97xAjaEu9Ae6VqPabTjR7Zo03xUX5iaomvNtw33uww/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="400" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /><span style="font-size:auto; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">（图片：《京华时报》）</span></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">之所以对中国船员下此狠手，皆因为他对中国人的仇视――</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <blockquote style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">唯独中国船只拒绝向糯康交保护费；</span></p>
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中方经常联合泰国、缅甸、老挝展开缉毒行动，破坏糯康财路；</span></p>
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中国政府大力推进“替代种植”项目，很多当地农民弃种罂粟，糯康认为替代种植让自己的毒品生意釜底抽薪；</span></p>
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       </blockquote>
       <blockquote style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一名中国商人在老挝兴建金木棉赌场，极大冲击了糯康旗下天堂赌场的生意。</span></p>
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        <p style="min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">……</span></p>
       </blockquote>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">由此，糯康产生了疯狂报复的念头。2011年4月，糯康绑架了13名在金木棉经济区工作的中国人员，在收取830万美元赎金之后，才放了人。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">仅仅在6个月之后，糯康又把魔爪伸向13名无辜的中国船员，将他们全部杀害，无一生还。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.6624203821656051" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANKqHR56371OEB3LgBc8sYOA73NIzhyFCh2ncvUicvpvQMsfUMN8OEZxQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="471" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">惨案发生之后，中方很快确定了糯康的嫌疑人身份，并展开了对糯康集团的抓捕。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这并不是一件容易的事。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">糯康为了在当地生存发展，经常拿钱出来贿赂当地的基层军人、警察和“村干部”，对当地老百姓施与小恩小惠。一旦传出要抓糯康的消息，都会有人给他通风报信。<span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">（《京华时报》）</span></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.7168316831683168" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANtDAoHvYWFYV8oDaiaNvia2SyFcPl8icgZfmJHHGRhXn4ocibjY7KQITmicw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="505" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">想要抓到糯康，难度可想而知。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“10.5”案件专案组的张洪峰感叹道，“<strong style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">抓捕糯康比抓本&middot;拉登还难。</strong>”</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为尽快将糯康缉拿归案，专案组决定，把抓捕消息的知密范围压缩到最小，不让风声再有泄露的可能。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">同时，从糯康联系最紧密的人入手，斩断其手足。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="1.0340909090909092" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANa6VjXJTC06biahuF2LEuEQsQVxtZ8Ik1ia8YZA81tibl0GAN38fgvmnWQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="440" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">天网恢恢疏而不漏。2012年4月25日，糯康及两名同伙乘船从缅甸一侧横渡至老挝孟莫码头时，事先和中方联合掌握情报的老挝警察突然现身，将三人擒获。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.746875" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANoDnTvXCqibxF2MSuJ9ZfZ7f5ibe3DaRXbCAhMt3opbFuELGkkNgNqVrg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="640" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /><img data-ratio="0.6078125" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuAN8icWsCa7PGb9gl6xfAVQrVBVDJNQicPseBbmysHEHHZfC4T7V4YCEnYg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="640" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">糯康被捕后，他的妻子、部下希望用高价将其赎回。传言称，他们的价码给了1000万泰铢（约合人民币200万元）。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">然而这并没什么卵用。2012年5月10日，糯康由老挝交接给中国，这个残忍杀害13名中国船员的始作俑者，即将接受正义的审判。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.7860169491525424" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANWAbZg2Vq6I7gvY4Q0270K8KAymIvRMCsJrW49Uibuia14ZymJJpicAzwg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="472" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">糯康最后的结局是死刑。2013年3月执行。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">只有这样的结局，才得以告慰逝去的13名中国船员，才能给死难家属一个交代。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><iframe class="video_iframe" data-vidtype="2" height="502.5" width="670" frameborder="0" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?vid=r1309n1t5wx&amp;width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" style="display: block; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 670px !important; height: 502.5px !important;"></iframe><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">回过头来看，糯康集团的落网，专案组人员付出了巨大的努力。当电影还原更多抓捕细节之后，人们才发现背后有那么多惊心动魄的故事。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">而这些惊心动魄，往往就是缉毒警察的日常。</span><span style="font-size:auto; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">他们要冒着各种危险抓捕毒贩，不能公开身份，也不能暴露照片，否则，可能会遭到打击报复，甚至危及家人。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-ratio="0.33754512635379064" data-s="300,640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdHpHMYRdfr2rOYdohTpWJfbM6S3xuANlVVicK9wOEdLC0lHrdKS2LBo7j8HPdTGgoE6icAOvrg9evBAT5hj16OQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">哥不想在这里谈毒品的危害，因为我们已经见过太多了，哥只想说，<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">面对那些吸毒的人，不要轻言原谅，因为他们每一口毒品，都可能浸染缉毒警察的鲜血。</strong></span></span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这是真的。</span></p>
       <p style="min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
